Definition: marked by quiet and caution and secrecy
Example: taking pains to avoid being observed; a furtive manner; a sneak attack; stealthy footsteps; a surreptitious glance at his watch
Synonyms: noun, attribute, furtiveness, sneak, a, person, sneaky, sneakiness, stealthy, act, stealth, stealthiness, surreptitious, marked, by, quiet, and, caution, secrecy, taking, pains, to, avoid, being, observed, manner, attack, footsteps, glance, at, his, watch
Category: adj.all
